        {
            "title": "【過年前趕上車】過年前買家成功榮升做業主兼講價12萬  前業主538萬沽屯市 勁賺497萬",
            "description": "<div class=\"atoms\"><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><strong>上車客議價 12 萬趕農曆年前入市 屯門時代廣場長情業主持貨 38 年 帳面勁賺 12 倍離場</strong></p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">隨著農曆新年漸近，不少準買家為求趕及在歲晚前落實「安樂窩」，入市節奏明顯加快。屯門時代廣場近日錄得一宗成交，一名上車客在積極議價後，獲業主讓步減價 12 萬元，最終成功以 538 萬元承接單位，趕及在新年前榮升業主。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">閱讀更多：<br/><a class=\"link\" data-ylk=\"slk:屯門一月145宗交投 衝上全港第二｜豫豐長情客勁賺逾倍 屯市兩房微蝕跑輸大市;elm:context_link;itc:0;sec:content-canvas\" href=\"https://b.28hse.com/4rNhDmU\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\" target=\"_blank\">屯門一月145宗交投 衝上全港第二｜豫豐長情客勁賺逾倍 屯市兩房微蝕跑輸大市</a></p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><strong>買家誠意打動業主 獲減價 12 萬歲晚前上車</strong></p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">是次成交單位為時代廣場 A 座中層 5 室，實用面積 487 平方呎，採兩房間隔。中原地產梁健文表示，業主原先叫價 550 萬元，賣方套現意欲頗高，最終被新買家誠意打動，並讓步減價 12 萬元，議價後以呎價 11,047 元易手。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><strong>業主長情持貨帳賺 12 倍</strong></p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">長情業主早在 1988 年以 40.66 萬元購入物業，持貨至今長達 38 年，是次以 538 萬元沽出，帳面獲利高達 497.34 萬元，物業在 38年間錄得 12 倍的驚人升幅。<br/><br/></p><div class=\"bg-toast-background -mx-5 -mt-2 mb-3 pb-3 md:-mx-0 lg:mx-auto lg:w-[300px] lg:pb-0\"><div class=\"text-px14 text-gandalf py-1 text-center leading-5\">廣告</div><div class=\"mx-auto text-center min-w-[300px] min-h-[250px]\" id=\"sda-inbody-9259eabe-f564-3318-8b7f-5d6405be3465-1-iframe\"><div class=\"bg-dirty-seagull text-px12 text-dolphin mx-auto hidden items-center justify-center only:flex w-[300px] h-[250px]\">廣告</div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">根據 28Hse 最新數據顯示，屯門市中心一帶的交投表現穩健，過去 90 日屯門市廣場已累積錄得 30 宗成交，平均實用呎價約為 10,670 元。是次成交呎價略高於屋苑平均水平約 3.4%。</p><div class=\"recommendation-contents\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mb-2 h-[30px] w-[80px] rounded-lg\"></div><div class=\"no-scrollbar -mx-5 mb-5 flex overflow-hidden overflow-x-auto md:-mx-2 lg:mb-3.5\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mr-2 ml-5 h-[92px] w-[calc(85%-28px)] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg md:ml-2 md:w-[calc(85%-16px)] lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mx-2 h-[92px] w-[85%] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">現時28Hse有12個屯門市廣場放盤，其中一個呎價低至$8,596，單位為於4座高層，實用面積349呎，單位向東南。<br/><a class=\"link\" data-ylk=\"slk:【即睇屯門市廣場筍盤】;elm:context_link;itc:0;sec:content-canvas\" href=\"https://b.28hse.com/4bPaKgl\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\" target=\"_blank\">【即睇屯門市廣場筍盤】</a></p><a class=\"mb-module-gap\" data-ylk=\"elm:img;elmt:link;itc:0;sec:content-canvas;\" href=\"https://i1.28hse.com/2026/02/202602131304335063544_large_nowm.jpg\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer nofollow\" target=\"_blank\"><div class=\"mx-auto w-fit\"><img alt=\"單位為梗廚\" class=\"rounded-lg\" height=\"240\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/sVWM1m1h8nmaMpXhAXdsgw--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTY0MDtoPTQ4MA--/https://media.zenfs.com/en/28hse_com_210/c9cdbe0a9e6ebcdfcdcc0d90b10a093a\" width=\"320\"/><figcaption class=\"text-px14 text-dolphin mt-2 wrap-anywhere\" style=\"max-width:320px\">單位為梗廚</figcaption></div></a><a class=\"mb-module-gap\" data-ylk=\"elm:img;elmt:link;itc:0;sec:content-canvas;\" href=\"https://i1.28hse.com/2026/02/202602131304337474097_large_nowm.jpg\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer nofollow\" target=\"_blank\"><div class=\"mx-auto w-fit\"><img alt=\"放盤單位位於高層，遠眺山景\" class=\"rounded-lg\" height=\"240\" src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/XOebUSkgpf9e1_15oA5wCw--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTY0MDtoPTQ4MA--/https://media.zenfs.com/en/28hse_com_210/67ce3bf579636746979d218eb67b0b48\" width=\"320\"/><figcaption class=\"text-px14 text-dolphin mt-2 wrap-anywhere\" style=\"max-width:320px\">放盤單位位於高層，遠眺山景</figcaption></div></a><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">同時，該區租務市場亦保持高度活躍，近三個月錄得達 56 宗租務成交，兩房單位回報率穩持在 3.9% 的高水平。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">延伸閱讀: <a class=\"link\" data-ylk=\"slk:屯門市廣場;elm:context_link;itc:0;sec:content-canvas\" href=\"https://www.28hse.com/estate/detail/屯門市廣場-4433\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\" target=\"_blank\">屯門市廣場</a>     <a class=\"link\" data-ylk=\"slk:時代廣場;elm:context_link;itc:0;sec:content-canvas\" href=\"https://www.28hse.com/estate/detail/時代廣場-4458\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\" target=\"_blank\">時代廣場</a>     <a class=\"link\" data-ylk=\"slk:屯門;elm:context_link;itc:0;sec:content-canvas\" href=\"https://www.28hse.com/estate/detail/屯門-27309\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\" target=\"_blank\">屯門</a></p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">延伸閱讀:</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">* <a class=\"link\" data-ylk=\"slk:新聞連結;elm:context_link;itc:0;sec:content-canvas\" href=\"https://www.28hse.com/news/%E9%81%8E%E5%B9%B4%E5%89%8D%E8%B6%95%E4%B8%8A%E8%BB%8A-%E9%81%8E%E5%B9%B4%E5%89%8D%E8%B2%B7%E5%AE%B6%E6%88%90%E5%8A%9F%E6%A6%AE%E5%8D%87%E5%81%9A%E6%A5%AD%E4%B8%BB%E5%85%BC%E8%AC%9B%E5%83%B912%E8%90%AC-%E5%89%8D%E6%A5%AD%E4%B8%BB538%E8%90%AC%E6%B2%BD%E5%B1%AF%E5%B8%82-%E5%8B%81%E8%B3%BA497%E8%90%AC-74605\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\" target=\"_blank\">新聞連結</a>。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">* <a class=\"link\" data-ylk=\"slk:28Hse A